Text: Sorry, I'm sure you've worked a lot with this, but you can't just layer two songs onto eachother and say it's a mash up... Must let my poor ears have a  long vacation after this experience...
uh, yeah i can.  by the comments on mininova and other sites - and the fact that people are seeding this, i'd say yours is not the universal opinion.
and i didn;t work on it.  just a fan.

According to www.boingboing.net the creator of this mash-up album has been sued in a multi-million-dollar lawsuit by EMI. So what can we do about that? Well, one thing we can do is to keep file sharing this album! F-ck EMI...
